commands.name: az security security-connector devops githubowner list
commands.summary: List a list of GitHub owners onboarded to the connector.
commands.syntax:
az security security-connector devops githubowner list --name
                                                       --resource-group
                                                       [--max-items]
                                                       [--next-token]

commands.name: az security security-connector devops githubowner show
commands.syntax:
az security security-connector devops githubowner show [--ids]
                                                       [--name]
                                                       [--owner-name]
                                                       [--resource-group]
                                                       [--subscription]
